---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={`CV - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="Curriculum Vitae" />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<div class="hero">
				<article>
					<div class="prose">
						<div class="title">
							<h1>CV</h1>
							<a href="/HeeyunKo_CV.pdf" class="download-button" download>
								Download PDF
							</a>
						</div>
						<h2>Education</h2>
						<ul>
							<li>중앙대학교 의과대학 (2020 - Present)</li>
						</ul>
						<h2>Research Experience</h2>
						<ul>
							<li>IBS Center for Neuroscience Imaging Research (2025 - Present)</li>
							<li>중앙대학교 신경유전체학 연구실 (2024)</li>
							<li>서울대학교 JW Lee 글로벌 의학센터 인턴십 (2023)</li>
						</ul>
						<h2>Projects</h2>
						<ul>
							<li>NeuroXi Community Founder</li>
							<li>Aphrodot - GodJam Sleep Consulting Service</li>
						</ul>
						<h2>Awards</h2>
						<ul>
							<li>2023 디지털 헬스케어 해커톤 AI 센터장상</li>
							<li>TEU MED 4th 혁신 콘테스트 참가</li>
							<li>중앙대 LINC 3.0 스타트업 지원 프로그램 공식 벤처 클럽 인정</li>
						</ul>
						<h2>Contact</h2>
						<ul>
							<li>Email: eindel1217@gmail.com</li>
							<li>LinkedIn: <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/heeyunko-42b517256/">linkedin.com/in/heeyunko-42b517256/</a></li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</article>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	.hero {
		background-color: #ffd1dc;  /* 연한 핑크색 */
		padding: 2rem 0;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
		width: 100%;
	}
	main {
		width: 100%;
		margin: 0 auto;
		margin-top: 180px;
	}
	article {
		max-width: 960px;
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 1rem;
	}
	.title {
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		gap: 1rem;
		margin-bottom: 2rem;
	}
	.title h1 {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 2.5rem;
		color: rgb(var(--black));
	}
	.download-button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 0.5em 1em;
		background-color: rgb(var(--primary));
		color: white;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 4px;
		transition: background-color 0.2s;
	}
	.download-button:hover {
		background-color: rgb(var(--primary-dark));
		text-decoration: none;
	}
	.prose {
		width: 720px;
		max-width: calc(100% - 2em);
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1em;
		color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
	}
	.prose h2 {
		margin: 2em 0 1em;
		color: rgb(var(--black));
	}
	.prose ul {
		padding-left: 1.5em;
	}
	.prose li {
		margin-bottom: 0.5em;
	}
	.prose a {
		color: rgb(var(--primary));
		text-decoration: none;
	}
	.prose a:hover {
		text-decoration: underline;
	}
</style> 